quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  23,33,"Àwọn olórí t’ó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú ìjọ rẹ̀, àwọn t’ó pe ìpàdé Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn nírọ́, àwọn tí A ṣe gbẹdẹmukẹ fún nínú ìṣẹ̀mí ayé yìí, wọ́n wí pé: \"Kí ni èyí bí kò ṣe abara kan bí irú yín; ó ń jẹ nínú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń jẹ, ó sì ń mu nínú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń mu"
  23,34,"Tí ẹ bá fi lè tẹ̀lé abara kan bí irú yín, dájúdájú ẹ mà ti di ẹni òfò nìyẹn"
  23,35,"Ṣé ó ń ṣe àdéhùn fun yín pé nígbà tí ẹ bá kú, tí ẹ sì di erùpẹ̀ àti egungun tán, dájúdájú Wọn yóò mu yín jáde (ní alààyè)"
  23,36,Ohun tí Wọ́n ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fun yín (yìí) jìnnà tefétefé (sí òdodo)
  23,37,"Kò sí ìṣẹ̀mí ayé kan mọ́ àyàfi èyí tí à ń lò yìí; àwa kan ń kú, àwa kan ń wáyé. Kò sì sí pé Wọn yóò gbé wa dìde mọ́"
  23,38,(Òjíṣẹ́ náà) kò jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe ọkùnrin kan tí ó dá àdápa irọ́ mọ́ Allāhu. Àwa kò sì níí gbà á gbọ́
  23,39,"(Òjíṣẹ́ náà) sọ pé: \"Olúwa mi, ṣàrànṣe fún mi nítorí pé wọ́n pè mí ní òpùrọ́"
  23,40,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Láìpẹ́ ńṣe ni wọn yóò di alábàámọ̀.”"
  23,41,"Nítorí náà, ohùn igbe mú wọn lọ́nà ẹ̀tọ́. A sì sọ wọ́n di pàǹtí. Nítorí náà, kí ìjìnnà sí ìkẹ́ wà fún ìjọ alábòsí"
  23,42,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tún mú àwọn ìran mìíràn wá lẹ́yìn wọn"
  23,43,"Ìjọ kan kò níí lọ ṣíwájú àkókò (ìparun) rẹ̀, wọn kò sì níí sún (ìparun wọn) síwájú"
  23,44,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A rán àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa níṣẹ́ ní tẹ̀léǹtẹ̀lé. Ìgbàkígbà tí Òjíṣẹ́ ìjọ kan bá dé, wọ́n ń pè é ní òpùrọ́. A sì mú apá kan wọn tẹ̀lé apá kan nínú ìparun. A tún sọ wọ́n di ìtàn. Nítorí náà, kí ìjìnnà sí ìkẹ́ wà fún ìjọ tí kò gbàgbọ́ lódodo"
  23,45,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A rán (Ànábì) Mūsā àti ọmọ-ìyá rẹ̀ (Ànábì) Hārūn níṣẹ́ pẹ̀lú àwọn àmì Wa àti ẹ̀rí pọ́nńbélé"
  23,46,"(A rán wọn níṣẹ́) sí Fir‘aon àti àwọn ìjòyè rẹ̀. Ṣùgbọ́n wọ́n ṣègbéraga, wọ́n sì jẹ́ ìjọ olùjẹgàba"
  23,47,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ṣé kí á gba abara méjì bí irú wa gbọ́, nígbà tí ó jẹ́ pé ẹrú wa ni àwọn ènìyàn wọn?”"
  23,48,"Nítorí náà, wọ́n pe àwọn méjèèjì ní òpùrọ́. Wọ́n sì wà nínú àwọn ẹni- ìparun"
  23,49,Dájúdájú A fún (Ànábì) Mūsā ní Tírà nítorí kí wọ́n lè mọ̀nà
  23,50,"A ṣe ọmọ Mọryam àti ìyá rẹ̀ ní àmì kan. A sì ṣe ibùgbé fún àwọn méjèèjì sí ibi gíga kan, t’ó ní ibùgbé, t’ó sì ní omi ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú"